Amo 6:	<b>Overview</b><br><u>Amo_6:1</u>, The wantonness of Israel, <br><u>Amo_6:7</u>, shall be plagued with desolation; <br><u>Amo_6:12</u>, and their incorrigibleness shall end in affliction.
